    <p class="corpus-intro">The Buddy corpus is not a web scrape. It is a curated, tiered, multi-source pipeline — built specifically to deposit the coherence framework into the model's weights.</p>
    <div class="corpus-grid">
      <div class="cg-card">
        <div class="cg-icon">📄</div>
        <div class="cg-title">AIIT-THRESI Papers</div>
        <div class="cg-stat">151 papers</div>
        <div class="cg-desc">The full framework — from the Wike Coherence Law through all 37 singularity gates, π boundary geometry, and the biological coherence proofs. This is the physics core.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cg-card">
        <div class="cg-icon">💬</div>
        <div class="cg-title">Gary Chat Logs</div>
